  "description": "<div id=\"product-detail\">\n<h4>Application:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>For LS motor swap on older Chevy, GM, Pontiac, Olds, Buick models</li>\n<li>Fits LS based engines (LS1, LS2, LS3, LS6, LS7, etc.)</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Note:</strong> NOT fit LS4 engines</li>\n<li>NOT work on standard SBC or BBC engines</li>\n<li>For LS series engine swaps only. NOT direct fit</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Features:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>2 Bolts Collector Construction, collector Merge Spikes, gains over 20+ hp</li>\n<li>Excellent quality and durability to improve vehicle performance</li>\n<li>Shorty design for power gain from idle to mid-range RPM</li>\n<li>Tight tuck-in fit that allows fitment flexibility</li>\n<li>Cast from high silicon molybdenum ductile iron</li>\n<li>Extraordinary durability under high working pressure and temperature</li>\n<li>Great resistance against corrosion and oxidation</li>\n<li>As-cast finish for a factory appearance</li>\n<li>The accessories in the photos are included</li>\n<li>1 year warranty for any manufacturing defect</li>\n<li>No instructions provided; professional install recommended</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Technical Specifications:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Header Type: Short Tube Header</li>\n<li>Primary Diameter: 1-3/4 in. (45mm)</li>\n<li>Collector Diameter: 2-1/4 in. (57mm)</li>\n<li>Head Flange Thickness: 3/8 in. (9.5mm)</li>\n<li>Pipe Thickness: 16 gauge (1.5mm)</li>\n<li>Material: Hi-Sil Moly Ductile Iron</li>\n<li>Finish: Natural</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
